      "title": "Police curfew lifted",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police curfew which was imposed in several police divisions in the Western Province with effect from 9 pm yesterday, had been lifted.",
        "Accordingly, police curfew imposed in the Negombo, Kelaniya, Nugegoda, Mount Lavinia, Colombo North, Colombo South and Colombo Central police divisions was lifted at 8 am today, police said."
      ],
